China May Buy Hungary’s Forint, Eurobonds, Fellegi Tells Reuters

-- B y   A n d r a s   G e r g e l y
-- 
2011-06-30T07:34:41Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-30/china-may-buy-hungary-s-forint-eurobonds-fellegi-tells-reuters.html
China may buy both forint and
foreign-currency bonds from  Hungary  and the purchases will be
made under market conditions, Reuters news service reported late
yesterday, quoting Hungary’s Development Minister Tamas Fellegi.  Hungary plans to keep the government’s stake in the
country’s biggest refiner Mol Nyrt. “for now”, Reuters said,
citing Fellegi.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andras Gergely in Budapest 
